Last Updated:
December 2024
This privacy policy describes how HyperBeard, Inc. and its subsidiaries (collectively, “HyperBeard”) collects, uses, and discloses information from players of its more complex games (“HyperBeard General Audience Games”). Please read this privacy policy carefully so that you understand our information practices. By downloading, accessing, and/or playing the HyperBeard General Audience Games, you consent to the collection of information about you, pursuant to this privacy policy.
Specifically, the HyperBeard General Audience Games include:
Penguin Sushi Bar: Idle Game
Meow MixUp: Sorting Puzzle
Tsuki Tea House: Idle Journey
Meow Tower: Nonogram Puzzle
Other games published by HyperBeard are not covered by this privacy policy. Please refer to the HyperBeard Mixed Audience Games
privacy policy
if the game you are interested in is not listed above.
If you are using our services through a game on Apple Arcade, please see our Apple Arcade specific privacy policy
here
.
If you are a California resident, additional privacy terms set out in
Appendix A
also apply to the processing of information collected in the course of your playing the games.
If you are located in the European Economic Area or the United Kingdom, additional privacy terms set out in
Appendix B
also apply to the processing of your personal information.
